Utterance.UttText: Martin Cavedon 73, bed 4, under Dr Sanchez, came in with chest pain with long history of heart problems, asthma and GORD.
His blood results just arrived and still for the doctor s review.
Please call the doctor for the results.
He is for carotid US to be arranged and for ECHO at some stage. all obs are charted, ECG done and he complaint of chest pain not too long ago and 2 anginine given with good effect.
He was also given morphine afterwards. he is stable now.
